<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">在有括号的加、减混合运算式题里,如果去括号能凑整计算，可以先去括号，再移位（移位时，数字和运算符号一道移），凑整先算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">532-(297-68)=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 532-(297-68)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=532-297+68</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=532+68-297</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=600-297</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=303</Run>
    </Paragraph>
 </FlowDocument>